{"tid":1262771,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony與Square Enix聯手打造《FINAL FANTASY》真人實景電視劇","createTime":"2019-06-28T00:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T15:48:53.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed85af06f3e8a63221f145b8a8f1048936aca83","tid":1262771,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368356456768195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2368356456768195&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=373ae742\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368356456768195</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDTzQTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDTzQTu.png&h=317675d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【業界】Sony與Square Enix聯手打造《最終幻想》真人實景電視劇<br />\n<br />\n  備受業界關注的RPG常青樹系列《最終幻想》即將登陸電視熒屏。Sony Pictures Television、Square Enix和製作公司Hivemind日前公佈消息（曾為亞馬遜製作《蒼穹浩瀚》，現也在為Netflix製作《巫師》系列劇）：公司將聯手打造《最終幻想》真人實景電視劇，<strong><ins>這次的故事設定於艾歐澤亞大陸，為原創劇情，引入了《最終幻想14》的設定</ins></strong>（艾歐澤亞大陸也是最終幻想14遊戲版劇情發生的大陸）。<br />\n<br />\n  傑森&middot;F&middot;布朗(《蒼穹浩瀚》)、肖恩&middot;丹尼爾(《木乃伊》系列)和迪內甚&middot;沙姆達薩尼(索尼影業即將推出的《血衛》)將為Hivemind製片。本&middot;拉斯蒂格和傑克&middot;桑頓擔任該劇編劇，並擔任執行製片人。 <strong><ins>Hivemind目前也在與製作人Lauren Schmidt Hissrich合作，為Netflix在製作遊戲改編電視劇《巫師》</ins></strong>。 Hivemind已與亞馬遜工作室就活動電視項目達成了初步協議。<br />\n<br />\n  這部新劇將融合《最終幻想》系列的人物和元素。 《最終幻想》系列歷時32年，共有15部主線作品，超過36部獨立作品。雖然新電視劇的具體情節仍未公佈，但<strong><ins>它將探索&ldquo;魔法與科技之間的鬥爭，為衝突中的土地帶來和平</ins></strong>。&rdquo;（這也是最終幻想系列大部分作品的主題，特別是14中）<br />\n<br />\n  最終幻想中標誌性的元素，如魔法，飛空艇，當然還有陸行鳥，都將包含在新電視劇裡。 FF系列熟悉的面孔和名字(包括FF系列幾乎每部作品中都會出現的某個希德)將會出現。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>【Square Enix股東大會要點摘要】前年度的手遊和頁遊情況非常不妙</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1249839/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1249839/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7272945255d827b4d1120b90b732768e1876c72f","tid":1262771,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7593104454f11786c423c443941af311e07fa0","tid":1262771,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7272945255d827b4d1120b90b732768e1876c72f","tid":1262771,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:36:26.000Z","msg":"又係巫師果組人搞，巫師選角好撚差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9709f196d795787c80263b042f482c90810e68f9","tid":1262771,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3348125b177ea0a8a0905e1ff5025b1d09d4f08a","tid":1262771,"uid":39365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"拉拉肥呢D點樣搵人扮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得真人化實仆街, 不如3D化仲好"},{"pid":"4d310a33cc8db2c3a69bafb84cb129d4d0d5ff9d","tid":1262771,"uid":18082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc7593104454f11786c423c443941af311e07fa0","tid":1262771,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7272945255d827b4d1120b90b732768e1876c72f","tid":1262771,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:36:26.000Z","msg":"又係巫師果組人搞，巫師選角好撚差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"好多時初頭話差 出到黎效果又好好<br />\n<br />\n例如最近阿拉丁咁"},{"pid":"8659b82c23eacb86cfd626cfee7b313c04a6411d","tid":1262771,"uid":43750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0